Package fr.cyu.chromatynk.parsing

Interface Token

All Superinterfaces:
PrettyPrintable, Ranged
All Known Subinterfaces:
Token.Keyword, Token.Operator
All Known Implementing Classes:
Token.And, Token.Arrow, Token.Assign, Token.BraceClosed, Token.BraceOpen, Token.Bwd, Token.Color, Token.Comma, Token.Cursor, Token.Del, Token.Div, Token.Else, Token.EndOfFile, Token.Equal, Token.For, Token.From, Token.Fwd, Token.Greater, Token.GreaterEqual, Token.Hide, Token.Identifier, Token.If, Token.Less, Token.LessEqual, Token.LiteralBool, Token.LiteralColor, Token.LiteralFloat, Token.LiteralInt, Token.LiteralString, Token.LookAt, Token.Mimic, Token.Minus, Token.Mirror, Token.Mod, Token.Mov, Token.Mul, Token.Not, Token.NotEqual, Token.Or, Token.ParenthesisClosed, Token.ParenthesisOpen, Token.Percent, Token.Plus, Token.Pos, Token.Press, Token.Remove, Token.Select, Token.Show, Token.Step, Token.Thick, Token.To, Token.Turn, Token.While
public sealed interface Token extends Ranged, PrettyPrintable permits Token.LiteralBool, Token.LiteralString, Token.LiteralInt, Token.LiteralFloat, Token.LiteralColor, Token.ParenthesisOpen, Token.ParenthesisClosed, Token.BraceOpen, Token.BraceClosed, Token.Arrow, Token.Comma, Token.Assign, Token.Operator, Token.Keyword, Token.Identifier, Token.EndOfFile
A lexical token. For example FWD 5% is parsed to Fwd() LiteralInt(5) Percent(), each token containing its starting and ending positions.
